            "title": "A股下滑   深股跑輸",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股早市報跌，深股跌約0.4%</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指開報3211點，平開，現報3210，跌1點或0.07%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指開報9957點，跌19點或0.19%，現報9937，跌39點或0.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300開報3778點，跌1點或0.03%，現報3772，跌7點或0.2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創板指數開報2006點，跌4點或0.2%，現報2003，跌7點或0.33%。</p>\n</div>",
