            "title": "港股開升87點  布魯可升逾81%  融創微盟挫近15%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數開報19328，升87點或0.45% ; 恒生國企指數開報7011，升32點或0.47% ; 恒生科技指數開報4335，升23點或0.54%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交34.27億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：布魯可官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241209_FI_source-web_Bloks-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：布魯可官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241209_FI_source-web_Bloks-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：布魯可官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">布魯可(00325)首掛升81.61%，報109.6元，一手賺14775元。今日同樣首掛的紐曼思(02530)跌1.25%，報0.79元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">同程旅行(00780)升2.79%，報18.4元，成交入20大。  </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紫金礦業(02899)商討收購，股價升</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">微盟(02013)挫14.78%，報2.71元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">融創(01918)插14.86%， 報1.49元，債務重組添變數。     </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">網易(09999)升1.11%，報146.3元 ' 美團(03690)升 1.18%，報146.1元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">安踏(02020)續升1.78%，報80元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)升1.19%，報76.5元 ; 工行(01398)升0.82%，報4.92元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14626131-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%8d%8787%e9%bb%9e-%e5%b8%83%e9%ad%af%e5%8f%af%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be81-%e8%9e%8d%e5%89%b5%e5%be%ae%e7%9b%9f%e6%8c%ab%e8%bf%9115",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/HKS_source-bp_.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-01-10 09:30:26",
